column5: Well Junior is two for two
Team racing is better than struggling with Wicked Stepmother.
Great start for the season, should be a great year for JR. looking forward to the Daytona race.

Two questions already answered before the season even gets underway. Will JR win this year? Yes Will Toyota win this year? Yes. Pressure is off for Toyota and JR. I was hoping Carpentier would make it into the show,he will be just fine this year I think. Tomorrow night is the truck race,the best racing in NASCAR.Go Johnny Benson. Joe
It's been a while since i watched a race...are they still turning left?
Most of our country is turning left.  All but me.
And I'll be there Sunday to watch it all unfold.
